title: The Legend of Mother Sarah (HomeUnix Manga) [English]
description:
I downloaded this a few months back and I wasn't to sure exactly what I was looking at. Were they single issues slapped together by a fan or were they official graphic novels? Regardless this collects Dark Horse's only graphic novel release of TLOMS, Tunnel Town, and what I assume is a scanlation of Delcourts release of The Legend of Mother Sarah graphic novels.

Includes

001 Tunnel Town 

003 Manipulation

004 Sacrifices

005 Suspicion

006 Deserters

007 Peace Talks

008 Betrayal

009 Deflagration

002 unfortunately wasn't part of the original download so hopefully you aren't missing out on too much without it.

Enjoy!
